# eof-quoted-key-no-value

## Input

```
"key"
```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..5
  ENTRY@0..5
    QUOTED_KEY@0..5
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@0..1 "\""
      STRING@1..4 "key"
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@4..5 "\""
```

## Syntax Error

```
[
    SyntaxError {
        message: "missing value for the key",
        range: 5..5,
    },
]
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: QuotedKey {
                open_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@0..1 "\"",
                string: STRING@1..4 "key",
                close_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@0..1 "\"",
            },
            value: none,
        },
    ],
}
```

